OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTencent's Riot Games cuts  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F11% of global workforce    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tencent Holdings' Riot Games has said  
OL,6, it will cut 530 jobs which account for 
OL,7, about 11% of its global workforce.     
OL,9,FIn a letter to its staff, CEO Dylan    
OL,10,FJadeja said "our costs have grown to   
OL,11,Fthe point where they're unsustainable".
OL,13,FLos Angeles-based Riot said teams      
OL,14,Foutside of core development will see   
OL,15,Fthe largest impact from layoffs.       
OL,17,FThe online gaming company says it will 
OL,18,Ffocus on its portfolio of live games   
OL,19,Fsuch as League of Legends, Valorant,   
OL,20,FTeamfight Tactics, and Wild Rift.      
